        <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
        <div>
            <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
                <div class="item active">
                    <h4>"Thank you for all the help you have given me with obtaining the mortgage. I will be sure to drop in and say hi when I'm over on holiday. If I purchase another property in future I will not hesitate to contact Lexus mortgages."<br><span style="font-style:normal;">Martin Pendlebury</span></h4>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <h4>"I wanted to take a moment of your time to thank you and your staff for the efficient and courteous way that you dealt with the business of obtaining our mortgage."<br><span style="font-style:normal;">Tracey Howell</span></h4>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <h4>"Please thank everyone for me. I will certainly recommend you to anyone I meet who needs help on this vein."<br><span style="font-style:normal;">Tony Harding</span></h4>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <h4>"Big pats on the back to you all……we will certainly use you again…excellent service."<br><span style="font-style:normal;">T Bell</span></h4>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <h4>"Can I say what an absolute pleasure it has been dealing with you. You've made what could have been a very complicated and stressful period quite straightforward. I can't recommend your services highly enough."<br><span style="font-style:normal;">Paul Johnson</span></h4>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Left and right controls -->
        <a class="left carousel-control mycarousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="right carousel-control mycarousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
    </div>
</div>
  

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 text-center">
                <h2>Let's Get In Touch!</h2>
                <hr class="intro-divider">
                <p>Give us a call or send us an email and we will get back to you as soon as possible!</p>
